{"id": "art-2501", "label": "Art. 2501", "title": "Art. 2501", "slug": "art-2501", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2078447028\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1737\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2078447028\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 250<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1770013602\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1736\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1770013602\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>Prevederile prezentului capitol referitoare la divizare, cu\n<span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span> art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>250\nalin. (1) lit. c)</span><span style='color:black'>, se aplic&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> atunci când o parte din patrimoniul unei <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> se desprinde <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\neste transferat&#259; ca întreg uneia sau mai multor <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>\nexistente ori unor <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> care sunt\nastfel constituite, în schimbul aloc&#259;rii de <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>\nsau <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;i</span> sociale ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nbeneficiare c&#259;tre:</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2051387733\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1735\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2051387733\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)<span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span> sau <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ncare transfer&#259; activele (desprindere în interesul <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>\nori <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>); sau</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_399723651\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1734\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_399723651\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)societatea care transfer&#259; activele (desprindere în\ninteresul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>).</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}